public abstract class GuiElementJsonBlueprint<Styles extends BaseStyles,Element extends GuiElement<Styles>,StylesBuilder extends BaseStyles.Builder<?>> extends Object
GuiElementJsonBlueprint provides functionality for building a GuiElement with its styles from JSON. Each blueprint should have a unique tag (getTag()).
